Expense Tracker App
A simple and efficient full-stack web application designed to split and track shared expenses among friends or groups. It automatically calculates who owes whom, making it easy to settle up.

Features
Dynamic User Management: Add and remove group members on the fly.
Expense Logging: Easily log expenses with the payer, amount, and a short description.
Automatic Calculations: The app instantly calculates individual balances and suggests the simplest way to settle debts.
Clean UI: A responsive and user-friendly interface built with React.
Tech Stack
Frontend: React.js, Axios, CSS
Backend: Node.js, Express.js
Data Storage: In-memory storage (for educational purposes)
